в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ api/all fetch calls to your Django backend
в”‚ в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ sensors.jsgetSensorData(), getHumidity(fieldId)
в”‚ в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ maps.jsgetFieldBoundaries(), getLayerData()
