в”‚ в”њв”Ђв”Ђ main.jsentry point вЂ” mounts App, registers Pinia & router
в”‚ в””в”Ђв”Ђ style.cssglobal styles
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ index.htmlsingle HTML file вЂ” Vite injects your app here
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ vite.config.jsproxy config вЂ” forwards /api calls to Django :8000
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ package.jsondependencies вЂ” Vue, Pinia, vue-router, Leaflet, etc.
в””в”Ђв”Ђ .envVITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000


